greetings my name is Matt Wood and I'm
here at the AWS headquarters in Seattle
to tell you about a new feature for API
Gateway API Gateway is a fully managed
service which makes it easy for
developers to create publish maintain
Monitor and secure apis at any scale
it's an API for apis that integrates
with serverless backends built using
Lambda or any of your other HTTP end
points we just made this a bit easy by
expanding our support for Swagger a
standard language for describing rest
apis with the new Swagger import API you
can replace or create a new API
automatically from a definition in
Swagger this allows you to easily
automate the creation and deployment of
your apis you can also merge multiple
Swagger files into a single API in the
gateway to help multiple teams working
on the same API simultaneously the new
Swagger import API is available to all
